    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Toyota 4Runner TRD Off-Road that perfectly balances rugged utility with everyday comfort. The exterior is finished in a crisp Super White that still holds a deep shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, faint scratch near the rear wheel well, the body is straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved. The black SofTex upholstery shows minimal wear on the driver\u2019s bolster and is completely free of rips or stains. All electronics, including the navigation system and crawl control features, function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the 4.0L V6 runs smoothly, backed by a complete service history showing oil changes every 5,000 miles. The frame is solid with only light surface oxidation typical for a vehicle of this age, and the BFGoodrich All-Terrain tires have plenty of life left in them. This is a dependable, non-smoker vehicle that has been cared for properly and is ready for its next adventure.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
